Package game.userInterface.applicationWindow

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutPanel  
    CharacterDialog
    This Dialog is used to let the use select the character that they want stored into in the field, When the button is pressed
    ChatBox
    This class represents chat box,it takes user string input then display in the textArea.
    PlayerNameDialog
    This Dialog is used to get the user player the player name will be stored in the playerName when enter key or the button is pressed
    ServerControlDialog
    This dialog is use to control the server (kill server,showing map)
    ServerDialog
    This Dialog is used to let the use select the server mode that they want (load,create new)
    StartingDialog
    This a dialog that make user select the game mode (run sever, start game , option)
    StatusBar
    Use for displaying players status (Health, current character)
